  "id": "RLSA-2023:7202",
  "summary": "Moderate: container-tools:4.0 security and bug fix update",
  "details": "The container-tools module contains tools for working with containers, notably podman, buildah, skopeo, and runc.\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\n* golang: net/http: insufficient sanitization of Host header (CVE-2023-29406)\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.\n\nBug Fix(es):\n\n* could not find symbol `criu_set_lsm_mount_context` in `libcriu.so` (BZ#2242871)",
